Ferrari's Challenges and Objectives

Ferrari has faced a challenging start to the season, compounded by a double exclusion in China. The team is currently 61 points behind McLaren. In response, Ferrari has set ambitious goals to enhance the performance of their SF-25 car ahead of the upcoming Japanese Grand Prix. ​
